  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the effects of short, psychological interventions on
      bio-psychological stress responses after an acute stressor. The efficacy of two different
      approaches (expectation-bases vs. acceptance-based) will be compared to a control-group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
